      • useablePeriod

        public java.util.ArrayList<SXCM_TS> useablePeriod
        A GTS specifying the periods of time during which the address can be used. This is used to specify different addresses for different times of the year or to refer to historical addresses.

      • use

      • isNotOrdered

        public java.lang.Boolean isNotOrdered
        A boolean value specifying whether the order of the address parts is known or not. While the address parts are always a Sequence, the order in which they are presented may or may not be known. Where this matters, can be used to convey this information.
